=version 1
=resource Chat
=method put
=endpoint /chats/:id/ban/:username
=description Bans a user from the chat.

include ../../_mixins.jade

p Sets a user's role in the chat to be Banned.

h3 Parameters

table.endpoint-param-table
    tr
        td.name :id
        td.description The channel numeric id of the channel.
    tr
        td.name :username
        td.description The username of the user to ban.

h3 Possible Results

+result("Successful", "200 OK").
    "User is now banned."

+result("Errorful", "403 Forbidden").
    "Access denied"

+result("Errorful", "404 Not Found").
    "Channel not found."
